SUMMARY:Locker Room: Heated Rivalry x Challengers
DESCRIPTION:March 7\, 2026 // 10pm\n\n$12.21 Early Bird (LIMITED AVAILABILITY)\n$15 Tier 1\n$20 Tier 2/Door\nall prices + fees\nBUY TICKETS \nTRACKMEET PRESENTS: \nLOCKER ROOM — HEATED RIVALRY x CHALLENGERS \nFrom the ice rink to the tennis courts\, meet us in the locker room where we’re turning up the heat with a Challengers x Heated Rivalry club night 🏒🎾🥵 Sweat\, slow burns\, locker room glances\, and rivals who are definitely gonna kiss… or at least make you wish they would. \nWe’re soundtracking the night with music from the TV show and the film\, plus pop and house tracks you def want blasting. Expect steamy fan edits on screen\, good music all night\, and a few surprises we’re keeping between us (for now). \nBring your boyfriend. \nBring your boyfriend’s boyfriend. \nBring the guy you’re “just friends” with\, but lowkey wish was your boyfriend. \nDress code: hot and sexy! tennis and hockey! \nSee you at the cottage 💋 \n 
URL:https://buddiesinbadtimes.com/event/locker-room-heated-rivalry-x-challengers/
LOCATION:Tallulahs
END:VEVENT
